              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The ORELA measurements were made using a 28 nsec",
                "accelerator burst width with a pulse rate of 600",
                "bursts/sec. The neutrons produced by a (gamma,n)",
                "reaction on tantalum were moderated in a 3 cm thick",
                "slab of water 15 cm in diameter around the target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Transmission data were taken on three different metal",
                "samples at liquid nitrogen temperature (77 K) having",
                "inverse thicknesses of 41.19, 175.5, and 763.9",
                "barns/atom. The metal samples were made at Los",
                "Alamos and were originally prepared for thermal cross",
                "section measurements on the Materials Testing Reactor",
                "fast chopper."
              ]
            }
